{"tid":2514144,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"審計報告促入境處查核假結婚　帳委會：暫不公開聆訊","createTime":"2021-05-03T05:26:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T05:40:52.000Z","uid":177556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b6caa529e60ca21d2b41da75e97eb2153f3e0ae5","tid":2514144,"uid":177556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:26:03.000Z","msg":"審計報告早前指，入境處應加快查核懷疑假結婚的案件。立法會政府帳目委員會開會後，指檢視過衡工量值及對社會影響等因素後，決定暫不召開公開聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n立法會政府帳目委員會主席石禮謙：「我們看過所有報告後，覺得這些都是很平常，尤其是從衡工量值的角度，影響不是太大。從良好管治方面，有些地方需要更正，我們現在的決定是暫時不召開公開聆訊。」<br />\n<br />\n帳委會又指，將就審計報告涉及的七個章節，向相關部門提出書面質詢，視乎回應，再決定會否召開聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n入境處早前回應審計報告，指對不懂刑事調查的人，胡亂批評執法部門的個案處理手法，嚴重破壞入境處的專業形象，表示遺憾。審計署亦罕有發聲明，指部門首長應避免公開反駁審計結果。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=433342\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433342&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOPG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=34078878\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433342&h=ea74ee27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=433342</a>"},{"pid":"2cbed00a3fe595bfe46e19d57903ab67ee87088c","tid":2514144,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:27:33.000Z","msg":"有炮真係大撚哂"},{"pid":"f28eeebc2836edd3d683241c1ea3d8a5f4ba4679","tid":2514144,"uid":274921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}